body:
Last 10 champion releases: Jhin, Aurelion Sol, Taliyah, Kled, Ivern, Camille, Xayah, Rakan, Kayn, Ornn.

{{champion:136}} has a displacement on his ult, depending on the distance between his stars and your champ;
{{champion:163}} has a knockup/displacement on her W;
{{champion:240}} has 2 small displacements, Q and R;
{{champion:427}} Daisy has a 3-hit AoE knockup;
{{champion:164}} has a small displacement on her E;
{{champion:497}} his W is an AoE knockup;
{{champion:141}} Rhaast&#039;s W is an AoE knockup;
{{champion:516}} E and R are AoE knockups.

Since the next champ is designed by CertainlyT, I&#039;m fairly sure that it&#039;ll have a knockup as well. 
I don&#039;t like this trend of giving knockups to every possible champion kit, at least until we get a way to counter those hard CCs since tenacity doesn&#039;t affect them.

I miss CCs that can be cleansed/reduced. If you get chain-CC&#039;d by multiple knockups you can just go afk because there&#039;s nothing you can do about it.
